<paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>We have received both your payment and waiver. Thank you!</font></paragraph>
